---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import ImageComparisonSlider from "../../components/ImageComparisonSlider.astro";
---

<Layout title="Image Comparison Slider">
	<div class="container">
		<section class="section">
			<p>The Image Comparison Slider allows users to compare two images by dragging a slider to reveal before/after states. Perfect for showcasing transformations, improvements, or differences between two versions.</p>
			
			<h2>Demo</h2>
			<div class="component-demo">
				<h3>Before & After Comparison</h3>
				<ImageComparisonSlider
					beforeSrc="https://placehold.co/800x500/ef4444/ffffff?text=Before"
					afterSrc="https://placehold.co/800x500/10b981/ffffff?text=After"
					beforeCaption="Before"
					afterCaption="After"
				/>

				<h3>Product Comparison</h3>
				<ImageComparisonSlider
					beforeSrc="https://placehold.co/800x500/6366f1/ffffff?text=Version+1"
					afterSrc="https://placehold.co/800x500/f59e0b/ffffff?text=Version+2"
					beforeCaption="Version 1"
					afterCaption="Version 2"
				/>
			</div>

			<h3>Features</h3>
			<ul>
				<li>Interactive drag slider for comparison</li>
				<li>Smooth transitions and animations</li>
				<li>Touch-friendly for mobile devices</li>
				<li>Keyboard accessible</li>
				<li>Customizable labels</li>
				<li>Responsive design</li>
				<li>Works with any image format</li>
			</ul>

			<h3>Usage Example</h3>
			<pre><code>&lt;ImageComparisonSlider
  beforeSrc="path/to/before.jpg"
  afterSrc="path/to/after.jpg"
  beforeCaption="Before"
  afterCaption="After"
/&gt;</code></pre>

			<h3>Use Cases</h3>
			<ul>
				<li>Before/after transformations</li>
				<li>Product comparisons</li>
				<li>Design evolution showcases</li>
				<li>Progress demonstrations</li>
				<li>A/B testing results</li>
			</ul>

			<h3>Interaction</h3>
			<p>Users can drag the slider handle or click anywhere on the image to adjust the comparison point. The component is fully responsive and works on both desktop and mobile devices with touch gestures.</p>
		</section>
	</div>
</Layout>